      • consume

        boolean consume(java.util.List<Token> tokens,
              Stream ps)
        Converts the input stream into one or more tokens that are added to the token list. In the lexeme, the tokens are potentially parsed out of the Stream and added to the list of tokens.
        Parameters:
        tokens - that are being generated
        ps - stream of data that is being consumed.
        Returns:
        true if text from the stream was consumed
